snippet.textDisplay:
They should add a Minotaur/Labyrint style gametype!

It's set in the jedi temple during order 66. All players except one play as jedi younglings, their goal is simply to navigate the temple and to stay alive.

The one player spawns as Anakin Skywalker. In the top corner of his screen is a radar/map that shows the paths he can take within the temple, and his goal is to hunt down all of the younglings before the time expires.
snippet.textOriginal:
*They should add a Minotaur/Labyrint style gametype!*

It's set in the jedi temple during order 66. All players except *one* play as jedi younglings, their goal is simply to navigate the temple and to stay alive.

*The one* player spawns as Anakin Skywalker. In the top corner of his screen is a radar/map that shows the paths he can take within the temple, and his goal is to hunt down all of the younglings before the time expires.
